{
  "texts": [
    "From 2000 to 2024, thematic analysis reveals that significant developments mark the advancement of AI in breast cancer diagnosis and treatment.",
    "Key concepts such as Human, AI, Female, Breast neoplasm, Breast cancer, and diagnostic imaging have emerged as crucial elements in the research framework of this field.",
    "On the other hand, diseases, medical imaging, computer-aided diagnostics, learning systems, and image segmentation represent emerging or declining themes with weak internal development degrees.",
    "They are marginally crucial for developing the given scientific field.",
    "According to the Sankey diagram and keywords thematic map, as shown in Fig. 8, we observe that from 2000 to 2021, studies were more focused on applying computer-aided diagnostics for detecting and classifying malignancy and breast cancer."
  ]
}